  "title": "Draftsperson/ Senior Draftsperson #77420",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Marine/ Oil & Gas</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Draftsperson/ Senior Draftsperson</strong></li><li>Working Location: Loyang (Transport provided)</li><li>Working Hours: Monday to Friday, 9am – 6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $4200 + Variable Bonus (Twice yearly)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Create detailed drawings and documentation for new construction projects and retrofit orders.</li><li>Produce outline and detailed drawings to scale as per requirements from authorities or client specifications.</li><li>Create preliminary drawings based on sales quotations.</li><li>Draft single line, termination, and arrangement drawings according to the scope of supply.</li><li>Prepare and submit necessary documentation for vendor approval to customers and class societies.</li><li>Monitor engineering activities to ensure timely completion of all documentation.</li><li>Carry out additional tasks as assigned by the section manager or supervisor.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum NTC 2/3, ITE or equivalent with AutoCAD proficiency.</li><li>Background in Electrical or Electronic fields is beneficial.</li><li>Minimum 2 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Familiarity with ISO 9001 and ISO 18001 standards.</li><li>Proficient in AutoCAD (2D/3D) and Microsoft Office Suite (Excel, Word, PowerPoint, PDF).</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77420 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
